        <body>
      
		<p rend="align(center)">Finished</p>
		<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N. Y.</placeName> <date>9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> of Sivan &#40;May&#41; 1849</date>.</p>
		<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir&#58; I immediately dispatched the desired book to<lb/> you&#44; through the post. Since the post office accepted it bound&#44; I<lb/> did not want to damage it by tearing off the covers. It cost<lb/> 25 cents without covers&#44; and 20 cents&#44; <del>bound</del> for the binding<lb/> Deduct 20&#37;&#44; leaves 36 cents. Add the cost of the Postage&#44;<lb/> six cents&#44; leaves 42 cents. Please write to me about it.<lb/> I give you 20&#37; rebate&#44; just as you do for me in your<lb/> publications. Nevertheless&#44; if you agree to work for my book<lb/> business&#44; I shall gladly offer you the highest rebate&#44;<lb/> which is 30&#37;. I still have not received the <date>May</date> issue of<lb/> the &#8220;Occident&#8221;. Please send me the <date>June</date> issue immedi<lb/>ately upon publication. I have just printed a catalogue<lb/> of my books and shall send you a copy with my next<lb/> number of the &#8220;Herald&#8221;. Do you want to advertise<lb/> it&#63; And can you add it to the &#8220;Occident&#8221;&#63;<lb/> If so&#44; I urge your response by return mail and I shall<lb/> send you 300 copies by express.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I want to tell you that <persName>Mr. Frank</persName> has begun<lb/> to print a prayer book with English translation&#44; of the German<lb/> and Polish ritual. When this is done&#44; perhaps you will want<lb/> to lower the price of yours before hand. I however&#44; don&#39;t<lb/> want to advise you about this. Nor do I desire to cause<lb/> a loss to <persName>Mr. Frank.</persName> Nevertheless&#44; since this matter is no<lb/> secret and will soon be publicly announced&#44; I consider<lb/> it my duty to call your attention to it.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">With all respect&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Devotedly yours&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">Isidor Bush</persName></p>
          
        </body>
